import numpy.random as npr

def data_stream():
    rng = npr.RandomState(0)
    while True:
        perm = rng.permutation(num_train)
        for i in range(num_batches):
            batch_idx = perm[i * batch_size:(i + 1) * batch_size]
            yield train_data[batch_idx], train_labels[batch_idx]
batches = data_stream()

opt_init, opt_update, get_params = optimizers.momentum(step_size, mass=momentum_mass)

def update(i, opt_state, batch):
    params = get_params(opt_state)
    return opt_update(i, grad(loss)(params, batch), opt_state)

def loss(params, batch):
    inputs, targets = batch
    preds = predict(params, inputs)
    #targets = one_hot(targets,2)
    #return -np.mean(preds.T[0]*targets.T + preds.T[1]*(1-targets.T))
    return -np.mean(np.sum(preds * targets, axis=1))

def accuracy(params, batch):
    inputs, targets = batch
    target_class = np.argmax(targets, axis=1)
    predicted_class = np.argmax(predict(params, inputs), axis=1)
    return np.mean(predicted_class == target_class)

import pyhf
from jax import grad
pyhf.set_backend(pyhf.tensor.jax_backend())

def jax_2bin(nn_pars, bkg_uncerts, pars, data):
    
    tensorlib, _ = pyhf.get_backend()
    
    sig = multivariate_normal(PRNGKey(11), np.asarray([2,5]), np.asarray([[1,0],[0,1]]),shape=(1,300))[0]
    bkg = multivariate_normal(PRNGKey(11), np.asarray([7,7]), np.asarray([[1,0],[0,1]]),shape=(1,700))[0]
    new_data = np.concatenate((sig,bkg))
    
    hist = np.sum(np.exp(predict(nn_pars,new_data)),axis=0)
    
    spec = {
        'channels': [
            {
                'name': 'singlechannel',
                'samples': [
                    {
                        'name': 'signal',
                        'data': tensorlib.astensor(hist[0]),
                        'modifiers': [
                            {'name': 'mu', 'type': 'normfactor', 'data': None}
                        ],
                    },
                    {
                        'name': 'background',
                        'data': tensorlib.astensor(hist[1]),
                        'modifiers': [
                            {
                                'name': 'uncorr_bkguncrt',
                                'type': 'shapesys',
                                'data': bkg_uncerts,
                            }
                        ],
                    },
                ],
            }
        ]
    }
    
    x = pyhf.Model(spec)
    
    data = data + x.config.auxdata
    data = tensorlib.astensor(data)
    pars = tensorlib.astensor(pars)
    return x.logpdf(pars, data)[0]
